    "en": {
      "title": "143 infected with Covid - 05 deaths",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today (29th) 143 new Covid-infected people have been identified, says the Government Information Department. Accordingly, the number of Covid-infected people reported from Sri Lanka exceeded 100 for three consecutive days.",
        "Along with the number of covid infected people reported today, the number of covid infected people identified in Sri Lanka so far has increased to 665 543.",
        "Meanwhile, the Director General of Health Services confirmed today that 05 Covid deaths have been reported yesterday (28th)."
      ],
